<h2>Uptown</h2>
<div class="info-image"><%= image_tag "uptown.jpg", alt: "Uptown" %></div>
<p>This is where we live! There's a bunch of good stuff around here. Here are a few:</p>

<ul class="restaurant-list">
  <li>
    <h3>Muddy Waters</h3>
    <p>If you're going to Uptown, definitely go here (we do all the time). Great beer list, good food, chill atmosphere. Not too pricey.</p>
